title: An S7 class to represent Dataset-JSON data — ds_json
text: creationDateTime Time creation file containing document. datasetJSONVersion Version Dataset-JSON standard. fileOID unique identifier file. asOfDateTime date/time source database queried order create document. originator organization generated Dataset-JSON file. sourceSystem computer system database management system source information file. sourceSystemVersion version "SourceSystem" . clinicalData Contains clinical data across multiple subjects. referenceData Contains non-subject data domains.
